                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17241014-17-defend90 t17241014-17-punish89"></join>
               Burnt in the Hand
            </rs>. And <rs id="t17241014-17-verdict90" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17241014-17-verdict90" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs> Pritchard and Risdel.</p>
